{"tid":1542623,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"推倒港共黑警的方向","createTime":"2019-09-05T02:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:14:40.000Z","uid":160588,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7edb381a7c3422db5cd9e8d42c24e88f5fdac1c0","tid":1542623,"uid":160588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"見到黑警喺狡辯會一而再再而三去遊花園、講大話、看圖看片寫故事，公信力一跌再跌。<br />\n要幫外國朋友解釋點解動議徹回唔收貨、點解黑警講左831太子無死人都無人信、點解咁多人相信新屋嶺污辱女性。<br />\n一句講就係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府同警方失去公信力</span></span>。<br />\n見到有文宣將林奠做官以黎講大話d事整合（囍帖街、碼頭、綜援等等）。<br />\n可唔可以幫黑警都整一set，比如撲低學生話地濕冼低，巴士飛走市民身份證話手抽筋等等。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住quote sources!</span></span>"},{"pid":"c983c1962e935880949d60655f4f1787d3c67f1d","tid":1542623,"uid":264717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/9gqgyVg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gqgyVg.jpg&h=9090095f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ea66f7f08f1a27719c8e22758bd483166d41eed","tid":1542623,"uid":160588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:09:07.000Z","msg":"尼d大話好多香港人都知都睇唔起但係外國唔知d黑警點對住鏡頭nak大眼講大話"},{"pid":"701331090eb40e033cf563f8392104e1a1d93446","tid":1542623,"uid":160588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c983c1962e935880949d60655f4f1787d3c67f1d","tid":1542623,"uid":264717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/9gqgyVg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gqgyVg.jpg&h=9090095f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"0de88278e064e4c3abafffb735a625b42dfa2eb0","tid":1542623,"uid":285368,"like":0,"dislike":